{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7da4def839","title":"毛泽东关于元旦社论和准备召开部分省委书记会议等问题的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f34cea9228","index":0,"year":1955,"month":12,"day":30,"articleId":"7da4def839"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"571e260848","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于元旦社论和准备召开部分省委书记会议等问题的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7da4def839"},{"id":"079534da34","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7da4def839"},{"id":"c10b57f36f","type":"appellation","text":"周、刘、陈、彭各同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7da4def839"},{"id":"a9e2b9bb2b","type":"paragraph","text":"社论写得很好，陈伯达作了一点修改，请酌定。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7da4def839"},{"id":"458b510a5e","type":"paragraph","text":"我已约陈毅、柯庆施二同志来此，先行商量一下，准备一月五日开会的事情。陈云同志病情如何?不知一月四日能来此否?如未愈，则不要来。谭震林、廖鲁言请通知他们于三日或者四日来此。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7da4def839"},{"id":"ceb72739af","type":"paragraph","text":"请周要尚昆用电话通知辽宁、山西、甘肃、陕西、四川，华东五省，中南六省的省委书记于一月四日到达杭州，准备于五日开始开会两天到三天，谈十七条的增加修改问题。除皖、苏、赣、闽可坐火车或汽车来此外，其余凡可用飞机的，要替他们准备飞机。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7da4def839"},{"id":"f29b971f86","type":"paragraph","text":"为《中国农村的社会主义高潮》一书写的一篇序言，请审阅，看是否可用。如有修改，请告田家英同志。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7da4def839"},{"id":"60f4a2d591","type":"paragraph","text":"敬礼","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7da4def839"},{"id":"2529221998","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东十二月卅日","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7da4def839"}],"page":{"id":"85bab989c2","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7da4def839","start"